snippet.title: Johnny Depp Reacts To Being Left Out Of NEW Pirates & The Caribbean...
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Reacts To Being Left Out Of NEW Pirates & The Caribbean...
The court and public battle between Amber Heard and Johnny has been raging on for so long that it's honestly hard to pinpoint where certain things began and where certain things have ended. But with every victory or delay or defeat that has happened, both sides have helped make it clear exactly where they stand on certain things. And that is again apparent because of the recent "victory" that Johnny Depp got by coming and reclaiming one of his most popular roles via Jack Sparrow, albeit in a video game setting. But in this "small" of a victory is enough to set a certain someone off. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation with Amber Heard and how she's reacting to Johnny's "comeback". Are you surprise by what Amber is doing? Or do you think at this point she's trying everything she can to go change the narrative in order for her to be seen as "real" and Johnny as a "bad man"? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
